data.description: Discover the essence of luxurious living in this magnificent single family home nestled within a vibrant and sought-after neighborhood. Boasting an array of desirable features, this residence presents ample space, ideal for hosting gatherings and cherished moments. Its inviting ambiance extends to the outdoor space, perfect for delightful BBQs with loved ones. Situated strategically, this haven ensures convenience with proximity to public transportation, highways, restaurants, and shopping destinations, embodying a perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Ideal for first-time homeowners seeking a nurturing environment with top-notch schools or astute investors eyeing a multi-family home opportunity (R5 zoning), this property radiates potential. Seize this remarkable chance to own a home that not only exceeds expectations but also promises a future of endless possibilities. Sold as is. HOME WILL COME WITH PREFERRED HOME WARRANTY! HOME NEEDS TLC
